#3030
The Convergence Rotunda~
At the geometric heart of Midgaard stands a circular rotunda under a brass-domed ceiling, engraved with maps of roads, catacombs, and stranger frontiers. Archways of distinct stone frame each route: ironbound stairs to the Public Dungeon, a soot-dark crypt passage, a rune-cracked vault road toward Kel'Shadra, a spiral stair to the Sepulcher Pasture, and a humming brass hatch into the Microcosm. Every path feels intentional, as if the city planners built this chamber to tame the unknown by naming every threshold.~
~
